name: Baby Doge Cash
public_notice: Kindly note that there are multiple, distinct projects that share variations of the moniker "Baby Doge". Users are advised to DYOR.

description.en:
Auto yield and liquidity generation protocol.
On each transaction, the protocol automatically distributes rewards to holders as well as auto-locks a portion of the fees as liquidity.​
The project aims to donate a high percentage of it's revenue to dog shelters around the world.
